g incagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background mr brian z france has been the chairman of the board and chief executive officer of national association for stock car auto racing inc nascar since october  mr france has been actively involved in nascar for more than two decades he has an extensive background in nascar ranging from his experience as a race track manager he served as nascars executive vice president since  and served as its senior vice president since  he served as nascars vice  president of marketing and corporate communications since december  he served as manager of group projects of international speedway corp since february  he served as vice chairman of nascar since  he has been a director of international speedway corp since  he serves as chairman of nascars diversity council an organization comprised of motorsports executives focused on encouraging greater diversity within the industry in  the sports business daily named france its sports industrialist of the year and sales and marketing executives international smei named him the smei marketing statesman of the year his previous awards include advertising age honoring france as one of the publications top  marketers of the year and promo magazine naming him as one of that publications top promoters of the year in  he was named to the broadcasting and cable hall of fameread full background corporate headquarters one daytona boulevarddaytona beach florida united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentdirectorinternational speedway corporationpresentchairman and chief executive officernational association for stock car auto racing inc education there is no education data available other affiliations international speedway corporation annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total comp